WEBVTT

00:00.339 --> 00:03.661
- Merry Christmas!
- Merry Christmas!

00:03.671 --> 00:05.446
Merry Christmas, George!

00:05.580 --> 00:08.452
Merry Christmas, movie house!

00:11.059 --> 00:14.132
Have you ever wondered what
marks our time here...

00:16.043 --> 00:19.394
if one life can really make
an impact on the world...

00:20.031 --> 00:22.793
or if the choices
we make matter?

00:24.929 --> 00:28.444
Sometimes, in order to move forward,
you have to go back.

00:31.819 --> 00:35.747
In this case,
just a few minutes.

